      {
        "id": "IVT.8-orderPackaging",
        "path": "IVT.8-orderPackaging",
        "short": "Order Packaging",
        "definition": "This field contains the primary packaging unit by which the item can be requisitioned or ordered to replenish the inventory supply item for the corresponding inventory location specified in _IVT-2, Inventory Location Identifier_. See {{v2-table:0818:Package}} as described in _PKG-2 Packaging Units_, and presented in Chapter 2C, Code Tables, for suggested values.",
